Author: Whypay
Text: I dreamed I was eating a family bag of Doritos once and when I woke up, I'd been taking orange, plastic battery insulators out of a box and chewing on them. Six different colours in the box but I was only trying to eat the orange ones.

Author: invisiblefatty4003
Text: I flip between enjoying eating as much as I want and enjoying it & eating then having a dream land panick attack about what I just did.
